data.description: This property has a lot to offer with extras all on one acre! 3BR/2BA, Fuqua home sitting on stem wall foundation. Inside you will find an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and picture windows overlooking extensive backyard. New flooring throughout installed July 2023. New range/oven. Under cabinet lighting in Kitchen. Property backs to very large ranch resulting in a quiet and very private setting. Extra deep attached garage that is 19x27, separate 24x24 shop with 220 service. An R/V cover in front along with 2 RV hook-ups. Two large storage containers that are covered. There is a ton of storage on this property. Complete inside Paint  completed 9/23. Bring all your toys!
